\hat{A}^2
x\frac{\mathrm{d}}{\mathrm{d}x}
\hat{A}=\frac{\mathrm{d}}{\mathrm{d}x}+x
\hat{A}^2=\frac{\mathrm{d^2}}{\mathrm{d}x^2}+2x\frac{\mathrm{d}}{\mathrm{d}x}+x^2+1
f(x)
\hat Af=\frac {df}{dx}+xf
\hat A^2f=\hat A\left(\frac {df}{dx}+xf\right)=\frac {d^2f}{dx^2}+\left(f+x\frac {df}{dx}\right)+x\frac {df}{dx}+x^2f
